    public class GeneralTransition
extends PropertiesList<javafx.beans.property.Property<?>>
    This is universal transition for all given properties. This will automatically generate transitions for all given properties and run them dynamically when property change. All what you need to do is create this object with and all given properties will be dynamically animated when you change them in code or even from CSS! So yes... just create this object and watch the magic and countless new opportunities!
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    PETO
